===Etymology===
Coined by {{w|Humphry Davy}} in 1807, from {{suffix|en|soda|-ium}}, "soda" being from {{etyl|it|en}} {{m|it|soda}}, which may be from {{der|en|ar|سُوَّاد|tr=suwwād|gloss=[[saltwort]]}} or {{der|en|ar|سُوَيْدَاء|tr=suwaydāʾ|gloss={{w|Suaeda}}}}.<ref>{{R:Oxford Dictionaries Online}}</ref>

